summary: This new code file, moviepage6.html, contributes to the system by displaying detailed information about a specific movie, "The Theory of Everything." It includes a movie poster, a summary of the movie plot, a video trailer, and a section for users to rate the movie using star ratings. The file also introduces a responsive navigation menu and a button for users to go back to the home page. Additionally, it incorporates external CSS and JavaScript files to enhance the layout and functionality of the movie page.
